data.description: This charming home is situated on a spacious lot. The home is featured with an astonishing brick exterior and fully updated interior. The interior has been remodeled with beautiful new flooring throughout the living area and white cabinets in the kitchen. The sliding glass doors provide a admirable view of the backyard, while also allowing an abundance of light to enter into the the general living spaces of home. The laundry room provides additional space for storage.
